	<PARAGRAPH ID="5">
		<SENTENCE ID="5.1">
			<STRING>The area, while still fairly inaccessible, was even more isolated until the recent development of El Chalten village and El Calafate International Airport.</STRING>
		</SENTENCE>
		<SENTENCE ID="5.2">
			<STRING>The mountain climb, however, remains extremely difficult and is the preserve of very experienced climbers.</STRING>
		</SENTENCE>
		<SENTENCE ID="5.3">
			<STRING>Today, when a hundred people may summit Mount Everest in a single day,  </STRING>
			<REFERENCE ID="13" PARAGRAPH-POSITION="52" PARAGRAPH-RECENCY="0" SEMCAT="mountain" SENTENCE-POSITION="14" SENTENCE-RECENCY="0" SYNCAT="np-subj">
